{"tid":2053251,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［港府最強反制］聯匯改掛人民幣","createTime":"2020-06-06T06:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T10:52:43.000Z","uid":63543,"like":66,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d8f13fc8b42fa34e94c39622de549a57833405","tid":2053251,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"美國明目張膽干預中國內政<br />\n對中國為香港立國安法說三道四<br />\n香港政府必須作出最強烈既反制<br />\n<br />\n而家中國如此強大<br />\n港幣有咩理由繼續同美元掛鈎而唔同人民幣掛鈎<br />\n<br />\n掛人民幣就係沽美元買人民幣<br />\n可以做低美金，打擊美國金融穩定<br />\n支持人民幣匯價<br />\n補充中國既美元儲備<br />\n實現人民幣國際化<br />\n全面實行中國好香港好既政策<br />\n<br />\n強烈要求金管局立即更改聯繫匯率掛鈎貨幣做人民幣<br />\n如果金管局唔肯改就係唔愛國唔愛黨<br />\n一定係因為外國勢力全面滲透左金管局<br />\n必須要重組金管局，實行全面管治權<br />\n全面管治權必須包含貨幣既管治權<br />\n<br />\n反對派同政府內部既港英餘孽一定會全面反對<br />\n建制派及商界，包括匯豐渣打等必須表態支持<br />\n打倒一切反對勢力<br />\n實現習主席中華民族偉大復興既中國夢<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186dce4c8a77aafe33a63a3133df6a11251ac118","tid":2053251,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fe935255c4ff186613fb657c4d97b8d1b94487","tid":2053251,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"推到波叔回應"},{"pid":"bd2448630331420743efce56a0311fb3b1877158","tid":2053251,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc10c2b79c89ac51bc106b57065c1477b9971ed","tid":2053251,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T07:07:23.000Z","msg":"我就最愛國, 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0438b0afeb8c9de3fcf52235f00ea4d74dca2a09","